text: Freilassing (), until 1923 Salzburghofen, is a town in Berchtesgadener Land, a district (Landkreis) in Upper Bavaria. Freilassing can be seen as the biggest suburb of Salzburg. == Related pages == * Freilassing, Geschichte einer jungen Stadt; Kurt Enzinger, Rupertus-Verlag 2003, == References == Category:Berchtesgadener Land
title: Freilassing
